{"type":"message","id":"d58c8842","parentId":"0d7cedd6","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:38:54.518Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_205f393fbf7249df8f2d567c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"601857|中国石油\n601808|中海油服\n600256|广汇能源\n600583|海油工程\n000852|石化机械\n600547|山东黄金\n601069|西部黄金\n600988|赤峰黄金\n000975|银泰黄金\n002716|金贵银业\n601899|紫金矿业\n9866.HK|蔚来-SW\nAAPL|苹果\n920876|慧为智能\n688111|金山办公\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773106734516}}
{"type":"message","id":"af9683db","parentId":"d58c8842","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:38:54.522Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_27c67d050ee44a68b4217b44","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773106734520}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f6ef317","parentId":"af9683db","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:38:57.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"金山办公在自选股列表中，需要使用 tushare-data skill 获取该股票的实时数据进行分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e6cbca3c80ed41fc89a54adb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 获取 token\ntoken = os.environ.get('tushare_token')\nts.set_token(token)\npro = ts.pro_api()\n\n# 获取金山办公实时行情\n# 金山办公代码：688111.SH\ndf = pro.quote_daily(ts_code='688111.SH', trade_date=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d'))\nprint(df)\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773106734522}}
